Welcome to Town Of Us Reworked %modversion%!

Town Of Us Reactivated but better! (hopefully)

This mod is a mish mash of code and ideas from different games, mods and forks, mainly from Town Of Salem, Town Of Us Reactivated and The Other Roles. Enjoy the chaos that comes out as a result!

If you want to know more try using the other info commands, visiting the %github% page or joining the %discord% server. Happy ejections!

Changelog-
- Update: Updated BepInEx to 6.0.0-be.682
- Addition: Added Attack and Defense values to roles, for simpler actions and explanations
- Addition: Added a loading screen
- Addition: Added next/back page buttons to guessing menus
- Addition: Added some countermeasures for the hacks that have been going around lately
- Rework: Pestilence has been reworked to work similar to Plaguebearer
- Recode: Interactions and Cosmetics have been fully recoded
- Recode: Saving and loading custom options have been recoded to be simpler to manage including being able to name your own presets (and no more slot limits!)
- Improvement: The hud buttons are a little more interactive
- Improvement: Improved the mod updater/downloader
- Improvement: LevelImpostor can now also be downloaded from the main menu
- Improvement: Bugs and bombs are now handled a little better to avoid any errors
- Improvement: Setting the "Max Fixes" setting to 0 will turn Engineers into regular venting crewmates
- Improvement: Reduced the load the mod puts for smoother gameplay
- Improvement: Scaled up the Grenadier flash range options
- Change: Ambushers and Crusaders now protect their targets too, making them double edged swords
- Critical Fix: Fixed settings being duplicated
- Critical Fix: Fixed postmortal roles not spawning in correctly
- Critical Fix: Fixed dead bodies not showing up on the meeting screen for non-hosts
- Critical Fix: Fixed the games not starting with 8 and byond players in the lobby
- Critical Fix: Fixed the "Fatal Error In GC" issue that has been plaguing us for months
- Role Fix: Fixed Whisperer conversions not syncing for persuaded players
- Role Fix: Fixed Engineer not fixing the mushroom mixup sabotage on Fungle
- Role Fix: Fixed Actor role lists not syncing correctly
- Role Fix: Fixed sometimes being unable to drag bodies as Janitor
- Bug Fix: Fixed the log spams that slowed the game down
- Bug Fix: Reduced the lobby load in times by a lot
- Bug Fix: Fixed not being able to zoom in
- Bug Fix: Fixed guess buttons not disappearing correctly
- Bug Fix: Fixed being able to lag role generation in Role List mode by setting a role list and ban list value the same
- Bug Fix: Fixed some more log spams
- Bug Fix: Fixed several desync issues
- General Fix: Fixed a couple of oversights in the code
- Visual Fix: Fixed the report button showing even when dead
- Visual Fix: Fixed the "Player does not have Town Of Us Reworked" appearing when someone is joining
- Visual Fix: Fixed the glass cracks not disappearing when switching between dead and alive players during a meeting
- Visual Fix: Fixed a small visual bug with flashlights
- Temporary Removal: Removed Submerged compatibility for now as it is really buggy, it will return next update

